author: Nintendo of America
description:
Defend the galaxy in MARVEL Cosmic Invasion, out now on Nintendo Switch 2 and Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/marvel-cosmic-invasion-switch-2/?utm_source=SW&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=P1021-01&utm_id=P1021-01 

A cosmic battle awaits! Choose between 15 Marvel Super Heroes in a new action beat ‘em up as you fight against the deadly Annihilation Wave. From New York City to the depths of the Negative Zone, travel across the stars to save the future of the Universe.
